# Plugin Registration

Centralize plugin configuration in `src/plugins/index.ts`. 
Use the exported `install` method to register router, store and other plugins with the app instance:
```typescript
export default {
  install(app: App): void {
    app.use(RouterPlugin)
    app.use(StorePlugin)
    app.use(NProgressPlugin)
    app.use(VuetifyPlugin)
    // register custom components and directives
  },
}
```

Add plugins by importing them in this file rather than directly in `main.ts`.